<item>
            <title>[DERBY-3107] On client, Clob.free() does not release locators.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3107</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On client, Clob.free() does not call the stored procedure to release the locator associated with the Clob. Hence, server-side Clob objects are not freed until the transaction terminates.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>All</environment>
        <key id="12379740">DERBY-3107</key>
            <summary>On client, Clob.free() does not release locators.</summary>
