                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12532616" author="oysteing" created="Fri, 5 Oct 2007 10:20:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch, derby-3107.diff, makes sure Clob.free() releases the associated locator.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I also added tracing of Clob.free() since that was missing.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12532617" author="oysteing" created="Fri, 5 Oct 2007 10:26:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Existing tests succeed with this patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It is bit difficult to write tests for this, but the locking tests that are added to jdbc4/ClobTest as part of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-3098&quot; title=&quot;LOB locks are not released after free().&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-3098&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-3098&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fails for client-server without this fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12534044" author="knutanders" created="Thu, 11 Oct 2007 14:09:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The patch looks good to me (but it adds two lines with trailing spaces). +1 to commit.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12534788" author="oysteing" created="Mon, 15 Oct 2007 09:56:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for the review, Knut Anders, I have committed the fix, but by accident, I ended up removing  all trailing spaces from the file, not just from the lines added by me.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will also port this fix to 10.3 (without the white space noise).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12534817" author="oysteing" created="Mon, 15 Oct 2007 12:02:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged patch into 10.3 branch as 584756.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
